Progresif Cellular Sdn Bhd (also known as Progresif) is a Brunei-based telecommunications company headquartered in Bandar Seri Begawan, Brunei. The company has more than 150,000 active subscribers as of October 2016. Progresif took over operations from the now defunct B-Mobile Communications.
Progresif has eight retail branches throughout the country and employs more than 265 mostly local staff. Progresifâ€™s business ranges from post- and prepaid residential mobile communication services to enterprise solutions for commercial entities. The company offers voice, data, and two-way text messaging on UMTS 2100 and GSM/GPRS 900 networks.
